Package databaseManagement

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckAppointment
    This class reads the booked appointments from the database.it can also read the priorities of the appointments
    DeleteEvent
    This class is used to delete the events of a user.
    DuplicateUser
    This class finds the duplicate entries in the database of user profiles.
    Events
    This class handles the events interaction with the database.It can read and write events in the database
    FileManagement
    This class can read and write a file from / to database.
    FindProfile
    This class finds the profile in the database.
    Participants
    This class is used for the entry and deletion of the table participant in the database.
    ReminderEmails  
    SecretKeyManager
    This class can upload and download the secret key of each profile to database.
    UserInformation
    This class can upload , download user's registration information.
